"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The x parameter in plt.text should be a numerical value representing the data coordinates, but a string representing a date is provided instead. The text function expects the x and y coordinates to be in the same format as the data being plotted, which in this case is datetime for the x-axis.\", \"patch\": \"17c17\\n< plt.text(\\\"2013-01-05\\\", 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n---\\n> plt.text(pd.to_datetime(\\\"2013-01-05\\\"), 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n\"}"